{"tid":1838320,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"年尾找數 po 有數齊齊找","createTime":"2020-01-24T03:38:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T04:07:22.000Z","uid":326897,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7590a8de822bbe557074be060228411299564cd4","tid":1838320,"uid":326897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:38:01.000Z","msg":"又到年尾，今年發生好多大事，<br />\n重有好多事都發生緊，<br />\n有幾多手應承過如果乜乜乜，我就乜乜乜<br />\n今日係年三十，有咩未還就唔好帶過年啦，<br />\n下年重有好多手足等我地，<br />\n咁就等我還先啦，<br />\n上次講如果中咗嗰<br />\n仆街政府除夕膠官一齊死抽獎活動，<br />\n我中幾多就捐幾多<br />\n我找數啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UMiN2a9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUMiN2a9.png&h=fd730327&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n派超市券都仆街過人，分兩間，咁其他嗰啲呢？屌你正廢柴，<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3JZBa41.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3JZBa41.png&h=24b19514&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中幾多捐幾多仆街政府維穩費，<br />\n全數入抗爭者手中，手足加油<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"82964291f28b0e0bd3109abcbebd0d5475665572","tid":1838320,"uid":626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:02:07.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"7d74ebaf984e68c77a5dce1d6c7dc342600b5327","tid":1838320,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:07:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"}]}